{"tid":940881,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過係tinder 溝返自己條仔/女？","createTime":"2018-12-14T09:51:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T10:50:17.000Z","uid":43208,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d945682f7e4438cd924390b8db0266f5d35b98c1","tid":940881,"uid":43208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T09:51:37.000Z","msg":"前度自從俾我發現左玩tinder之後，就飛左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後我發覺無論用咩方法，佢都唔肯同我講野<br />\n<br />\n初初都係叫d朋友係tinder 同佢傾下計<br />\n慢慢就直情把心一橫，扮第二個同佢傾計<br />\n點知最後佢真係中意左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我咁做既目的，從來冇諗過要報復返佢<br />\n但我好想知一d唔會用我真身問到既野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到底我係咪做錯左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa4d51e9f84d7e7cdfe1ae4b66bb01eefb3851ad","tid":940881,"uid":157363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T09:52:48.000Z","msg":"曝露身份同佢講係緣分 睇下佢仲鐘唔鐘意你先"},{"pid":"40d5cb3e5cde14143116bd4ca841cc6ffd3074e5","tid":940881,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T09:54:13.000Z","msg":"真定假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果係真 成件事好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e30e1814a0b270c271b2c4222731aa887e6d44f1","tid":940881,"uid":18521,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T09:55:36.000Z","msg":"有冇下文"},{"pid":"fd01afcf8d711d818d2f53ee963bd0bae49e9937","tid":940881,"uid":43208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40d5cb3e5cde14143116bd4ca841cc6ffd3074e5","tid":940881,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T09